- Nav: collapse home/work into single 'work' item; rename visual→playground; 3-item nav across all pages
- Nav pill: fade in after position snap to eliminate jump glitch on page load
- Landing windows: w1 clicks→work, w2→about, w3→playground; Intuit/Figma/Viget hyperlinked in tagline
- Cursors: dark retro pill with destination label for window CTAs (↓ work, → about, → play); friendly 🔒 error state for locked sidebar items
- Sidebar: hovering/clicking locked sections shows 🔒 cursor message instead of broken scroll
- Case study scrollbar: 8px wide, visible track, hover state
- Prev/next cards: gradient backgrounds matching case study colors with cover image overlay
- First section whitespace: reduced .mh margin-top (52px→4px) + .ms-section spacing pattern
- LibbyU: badge year 2025→2026, add password lock (libby2026)
- Password system: each case uses data[key].password instead of shared constant

